class Solution:
    def rearrange(self, nums):
        """
        :type nums: List[int]
        :rtype: List[int]
        """
        if not nums:
            return []
        
        n = len(nums)
        stack = []
        for i in range(n-1,-1,-1):
            while stack and nums[stack[-1]] >= nums[i]:
                stack.pop()
            stack.append(i)
            
        res = []
        for i in range(n):
            while stack and nums[stack[-1]] <= nums[i]:
                res.append(nums[stack.pop()])
            res.append(nums[i])
            
        return res
